    "description": "<p>GOH LEE ENGINEERING</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Swimming Pool Maintenance Guy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Criteria</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Singaporean</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Can take hardship and not scare of sun</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. No experience required</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Singapore Class 2B License and Personal Bike</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Work Schedule</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 6 Days Week - Monday - Saturday (7am - 4pm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Complete the assigned job sites of the day and finished work</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Sunday and Public Holiday Off</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Scope</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Maintenance and cleaning of Swimming Pool</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Assist in any ad-hoc duties as assigned</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interested Parties, please feel free to contact us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
